{"tid":2478594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（菲律賓肺炎）何栢良倡禁賓國印巴等地航班抵港","createTime":"2021-04-07T07:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T07:30:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9655b57d0028c9b56526a4a6c61a986afabcff","tid":2478594,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UcWwzd.Q13IDO9U5ulziGQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/TbfMw9Ot7Wi685r0iib2cg--~B/aD0xMjAwO3c9MTIwMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/health_concept_154/558dd9ccd5bdba1cedb8bdcdbc3e22cc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUcWwzd.Q13IDO9U5ulziGQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTY0MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTbfMw9Ot7Wi685r0iib2cg--~B%2FaD0xMjAwO3c9MTIwMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhealth_concept_154%2F558dd9ccd5bdba1cedb8bdcdbc3e22cc&h=dac0c713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港新冠疫情 (COVID-19) 有放緩跡象，本地個案持續零星，然而外國輸入個案不容忽視。港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良表示，近日由菲律賓、印度及巴基斯坦三地輸入的確診個案，以前日（5日）為例，15宗輸入個案之中，半數為N501Y變種病毒，若然香港不及時把關，現時有機會「清零」的走勢可能會逆轉，由變種病毒釀成第五波疫情的話，爆發速度可以很快。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良指現時把關措施並不足夠，未達至滴水不漏的防護，例如機場工作人員每隔14日才進行病毒檢測頻率太疏、檢疫酒店員工疫苗接種率低，倡政府務必防止病毒流入社區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/封關措施-半數輸入個案為變種病毒-何栢良倡禁菲律賓等地航班抵港-050000050.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%B0%81%E9%97%9C%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD-%E5%8D%8A%E6%95%B8%E8%BC%B8%E5%85%A5%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E7%82%BA%E8%AE%8A%E7%A8%AE%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E4%BD%95%E6%A0%A2%E8%89%AF%E5%80%A1%E7%A6%81%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF-050000050.html&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=abf24ce4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/封關措施-半數輸入個案為變種病毒-何栢良倡禁菲律賓等地航班抵港-050000050.html</a>"},{"pid":"a0d9668958cc2ca50